Package com.iontrading.mkv.bulkentitlements

Interface IMkvESNamespaceAvailabilityListener

  • @Keep
@KeepPublicClassMemberNames
public interface IMkvESNamespaceAvailabilityListener
    IMkvESNamespaceAvailabilityListener can be used to get notification about the availability and readiness of the Entitlement Namespaces.

        @Deprecated
default void onNamespaceCacheInvalidated​(IMkvESNamespaceAvailabilityListener.IMkvNamespace namespace)
        Deprecated.
        The cached entitlement results for the specified namespace have been invalidated.
        Application listeners can override onNamespaceUserCacheInvalidated(IMkvNamespace, Optional) to react to finer-grain entitlement cache invalidation.
        Parameters:
        namespace - the namespace to clean up.

      • onNamespaceUserCacheInvalidated

        default void onNamespaceUserCacheInvalidated​(IMkvESNamespaceAvailabilityListener.IMkvNamespace namespace,
                                             Optional<List<String>> users)
        The cached entitlement results for the specified namespace and users have been invalidated.
        Application listeners can override this method to react to finer-grain entitlement cache invalidation.
        Parameters:
        namespace - the namespace to clean up.
        users - the list of users to clean up. In case of Option.empty(), the entire namespace cache MUST BE considered invalidated.
